OL,3,CBritish man arrested after woman's
OL,4,Cbody found in suitcase in Colombia
OL,6,FA Bournemouth man has been arrested in
OL,7,FEcuador after the body of a woman was
OL,8,Ffound inside a suitcase.
OL,10,FMatthew Ashley Foster-Smith is alleged
OL,11,Fto have caused the death of 36-year-
OL,12,Fold Natalia Villalba in an apartment
OL,13,Fin the Chico neighbourhood of Bogota,
OL,14,FColombia, on June 18, local
OL,15,Fauthorities said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
