CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782751677
OL,3,CBritish man arrested after woman's
OL,4,Cbody found in suitcase in Colombia
OL,6,FA post on the official X account of
OL,7,Fthe Attorney General's Office in
OL,8,FColombia said the 46-year-old is
OL,9,Fsuspected of beating Ms Villalba to
OL,10,Fdeath before placing her body in a
OL,11,Fsuitcase, trying to conceal what
OL,12,Fhappened and fleeing the scene.
OL,14,FDorset Police are said to have been
OL,15,Famong the authorities that assisted
OL,16,Fwith locating him before he was held
OL,17,Fat Quito International Airport in
OL,18,FEcuador.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
