CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782751677
OL,3,CBritish man arrested after woman's
OL,4,Cbody found in suitcase in Colombia
OL,6,FIt came after an arrest warrant was
OL,7,Fobtained by prosecutors in Colombia
OL,8,Fand the issue of an Interpol Red
OL,9,FNotice, local authorities said.
OL,11,FCarlos Fernando Galan, Bogota's mayor,
OL,12,Fsaid that Dorset Police had assisted
OL,13,Fwith the operation.
OL,15,FHe added: "This painful case will not
OL,16,Fgo unpunished."
