OL,3,CBritish man arrested after woman's
OL,4,Cbody found in suitcase in Colombia
OL,6,FA Foreign, Commonwealth & Development
OL,7,FOffice spokesperson said: "We are
OL,8,Fsupporting a British man who has been
OL,9,Fdetained in Ecuador and are in touch
OL,10,Fwith the local authorities."
OL,12,FDorset Police was approached for
OL,13,Fcomment.
